---

This repository also bundles third-party libraries under ./libraries, each
retaining its own license:
  - GFX Library for Arduino (Arduino_GFX) — BSD 3-Clause, (c) Adafruit
    Industries and moononournation. A patched copy: the ST77916 init table has
    been replaced with the JC3636W518 "V2" panel init sequence required by this
    display. See libraries/GFX_Library_for_Arduino/license.txt.
LVGL (8.3.6, MIT) is NOT bundled — install it separately (see README) and use
the provided lv_conf.h.
